# AI Doc Router Rule

Use this rule as the routing layer. Keep implementation details in canonical docs.

## 1) Context7 Usage

Use Context7 automatically for external dependency APIs:

- Three.js
- Vite
- wasm-pack / wasm-bindgen
- TypeScript compiler/type-system questions
- IndexedDB / idb
- Web Workers API
- Web Audio API
- Rapier (`@dimforge/rapier3d-compat`)

Do not use Context7 for engine-internal behavior. Read local docs first.

